  <!-- EN: Powered shortsword -->
  <MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.label>动力短剑</MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.label>
  <!-- EN: A highly-advanced short sword. Commonly used by Glitterworld assault troops, the blade is coated in a field of ionized plasma, helping it cut through enemy armor.\n(Core SK) -->
  <MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.description>一种装备于闪耀世界突击部队的制式高科技短剑。剑刃上覆盖着约束状态的等离子体，可以轻易切开敌人的装甲。</MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.description>
