  <MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.handle.label>剑柄</MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.handle.label>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.point.label>剑尖</MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.point.label>
  <!-- EN: blade -->
  <MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.blade.label>剑刃</MeleeWeapon_PoweredShortsword.tools.blade.label>

  <!-- EN: Wraith blade -->
  <MeleeWeapon_WraithBlade.label>怨灵之刃</MeleeWeapon_WraithBlade.label>
  <!-- EN: Highly advanced melee weapon. When active it emits a constant stream of ionized plasma that can cut through almost any armor. It's otherworldly appearance earned it the moniker and inspired many norbal folktales.\n(Core SK) -->
  <MeleeWeapon_WraithBlade.description>一种高科技近战武器。激活时会发出持续的等离子射流，几乎可以穿透任何装甲。它超凡脱俗的外观造型为它赢得了这个绰号，并进一步激发了许多民间故事的灵感。</MeleeWeapon_WraithBlade.description>
